## Factorial Implementation in RiX ##
## Demonstrates recursive function definitions and conditional logic ##

## Recursive Factorial Function
Fact(n) -> IF(n <= 1, 1, n * Fact(n - 1))

## Test cases
val5 = Fact(5)   ## Expected: 120
val10 = Fact(10) ## Expected: 3628800

## Output results
PRINT(
  "Factorial of 5: " + val5,
  "Factorial of 10: " + val10
)
